Trustee of Barings Corporate Investors (NYSE:MCI), Grace Edward P Iii, buys 1,900 shares worth $29,296
According to Barings Corporate Investors's most recent Form 4 filing with the SEC dated Jul 24 09:20 PM, company Trustee, Grace Edward P Iii disclosed buying 1,900 shares at a cost of $15.42. At the time of this transaction (Jul 24), this trade was worth $29,296 in total. As of Jul 24, Grace Edward P Iii now owns 10,000 shares in total worth about $155,006.0. 
For the last few recent trades made by Barings Corporate Investors (NYSE:MCI) Trustee, Grace Edward P Iii, we have the following information:




SEC Form 4 filing: Feb 10: Bought 100 shares at the rate of $14.60 per share. Total worth of this trade was $1,460. Total number of shares owned as of Feb 10 were 8,100
SEC Form 4 filing: Jan 27: Bought 3,500 shares at the rate of $14.68 per share. Total worth of this trade was $51,395. Total number of shares owned as of Jan 27 were 8,000




